<h3 class='post-title entry-title' itemprop='name'>
Spotlight on Desiring Death (Evading Death Book 2) by C.P. Mandara and tantalizing Excerpt from the book
</h3>
<div class='post-header'>
<div class='post-header-line-1'></div>
</div>
<div class='post-body entry-content' id='post-body-4547279756955457404' itemprop='description articleBody'>
<div dir="ltr" style="text-align: left;" trbidi="on">
<div class="separator" style="clear: both; text-align: center;">
<a href="http://4.bp.blogspot.com/-_uLfNO5fW7I/VNXW-1GrhmI/AAAAAAAACfA/-5PId7x9n2Q/s1600/Desiring%2BDeath%2BFINAL.PNG" imageanchor="1" style="margin-left: 1em; margin-right: 1em;"><img border="0" src="http://4.bp.blogspot.com/-_uLfNO5fW7I/VNXW-1GrhmI/AAAAAAAACfA/-5PId7x9n2Q/s1600/Desiring%2BDeath%2BFINAL.PNG" height="400" width="250" /></a></div>
<div style="text-align: center;">
<br /></div>
